name: the linen bag - Natural with Nautical Mile label
description:
The linen bag is an innovative storage bag that keeps bed linen or other contents organised and smelling fragrant (optional). Made from 100% breathable natural cotton canvas, it features patterned lining and an internal zip pocket.

Outer Dimensions:
350mm d X 300mm w X 130mm h

Each set contains:
1 x Natural Linen Bag
1 x Nautical Mile label

Designed in Australia
FREE Postage & Handling for deliveries within Australia
